                            <comment id="75412" author="mhanafi" created="Wed, 22 Jan 2014 05:23:25 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I had create a directory that was only 1 striped fixed on ost00000 to make easier to debug. I think that is why you only saw ost00000.&lt;/p&gt;
</comment>
                            <comment id="75411" author="niu" created="Wed, 22 Jan 2014 04:51:06 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/8954&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/8954&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="75410" author="niu" created="Wed, 22 Jan 2014 04:50:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thank you, Mahmoud. The log shows that only the OST0000 has such problem, I suspect it because the edquot flag on OST0000 was set mistakenly by some sort of race.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="75390" author="mhanafi" created="Tue, 21 Jan 2014 22:15:05 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;i have uploaded the following debug trace files to the ftp site.&lt;br/&gt;
